{"tid":806732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《星島》：大陸「失信人制度」　高鐵香港段適用　港鐵曾爭取豁免被拒","createTime":"2018-09-05T02:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T03:04:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"198e61f56753ce67c9e60de2b7d8b6536a1d9816","tid":806732,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/TRUST2-01_bDXsL_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FTRUST2-01_bDXsL_1200x0.png&h=e05a2e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》今日引述消息報道，內地的失信人名單制度，即限制「嚴重失信人」不能購票坐高鐵的制度，會隨著高鐵通車引入香港，港鐵曾和內地商討，豁免由香港出發的北上列車，但內地指「難以妥協」而被拒。<br />\n<br />\n大陸在今年5月全面推行「失信人名單」制度，限制嚴重失信人坐高鐵或飛機，所謂嚴重失信是指在火車吸煙、擾亂車站秩序和行車安全、賣假票等行為，會被禁坐高鐵三個月至半年，而這制度亦會隨著高鐵通車引入香港。《星島》引述消息指，港鐵曾向內地方面建議，由本港出發的北上列車豁免採用這制度，但對方指這是國家政策，難以豁免。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/高鐵開通-星島-大陸-失信人制度-香港適用-港鐵曾爭取豁免被拒/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E9%96%8B%E9%80%9A-%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8-%E5%A4%B1%E4%BF%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9B%BE%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%2F&d=475R2aNBn2CFmojb1lVusTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4f5ec1ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E9%96%8B%E9%80%9A-%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8-%E5%A4%B1%E4%BF%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9B%BE%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%2F&h=11fc2120\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/高鐵開通-星島-大陸-失信人制度-香港適用-港鐵曾爭取豁免被拒/</a>"},{"pid":"65ffc9f0a4366a4fe2ae02b69b9ceff477d0610e","tid":806732,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.newsancai.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/53f8119b5bcfbf_8950221_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsancai.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F08%2F53f8119b5bcfbf_8950221_1.jpg&h=ba9a539f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c471171c0c0968ca02ba3856ce1345a14be17d7","tid":806732,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:03:48.000Z","msg":"一地兩儉現形了<br />\n<br />\n港豬遲d就會問：「點解我買唔到飛？職員又唔幫我」"},{"pid":"2845d5a42db2b0841dfd0ec87b10279d7ef9734e","tid":806732,"uid":100347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:04:21.000Z","msg":"政治逼害例如個仔食毒奶粉受害 家長要求個官負責 都會被blacklist"}]}